### Corpora

| Corpus | Description | Why |
|---|---|---|
| **Canterbury Corpus** | Classic text + code mix | Standard baseline for all compressors |
| **Calgary Corpus** | Older mix, historical baseline | Historical comparison |
| **Silesia Corpus** | Modern mix: code, XML, HTML, PDF text, DB | Realistic modern workloads |
