## 9. Key Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| GPU-CPU transfer bottleneck dominates latency | High | High | Profile early; use pinned (page-locked) memory; minimize round trips via larger batch sizes |
| Grammar compression memory blows out | Medium | High | Cap grammar table sizes; use streaming Re-Pair variant; shard large files |
| Context Island misclassification hurts ratio | Medium | Medium | Fallback: if island-specific model performs poorly, blend in a general model with low weight |
| rANS probability table overflow (quantization error) | Low | High | Use 12-bit tables (M=4096) for balance; validate round-trip on every build |
| CMIX-class ratio proves unreachable at practical speed | High | Medium | Reframe target: not to match CMIX, but to define a new Pareto front on the ratio/speed tradeoff |
| CUDA code portability (AMD GPUs) | Low | Low | Abstract GPU backend behind an interface; HIP port is a Phase 13+ consideration |

